div class="t m14da x71 he y35c ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">NoTE.—The Decalogue, the Ten Commandments, is the fundamental law </div><div class="t m117f x4 he y299 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of the church of God. It presents the chief ruler—God, the Creator of heaven </div><div class="t m3bfd x98 h25 yc50 ff4 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">[11 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
